============================================
Grim Tales 7: Color of Fright CE (2014) PC [FINAL]
============================================

- ENG

============================================
Description:                               =
============================================

It wasn't bad enough that your train was running late, but now a mysterious note warns that this Gray family dinner will be the last! Inside the Gray family castle, everything is in chaos, with your family nowhere to be found. Alfred scoffed at the corsairs by the fire. The walls are graffitied with the scribbles of a madman as his laughter echoes through the halls. Armed with a magical paint set, you are the only one who can save them. Reunite with previous Grim Tales characters, including Luisa, Elizabeth, James McGray, and even your niece, Jackie! Can you unmask the kidnapper and beat him at his own game? Find out in this mysterious Hidden Object Puzzle Adventure game!

============================================
Features:                                  =
============================================

Can the past be rewritten? Play the bonus chapter to find out
Check out your achievements and collections
An available Strategy Guide
Score soundtracks, screen-savers, and concept art

